# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SDLC Agent Platform — Environment Configuration
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Set ONE of the three backends below. Priority: Copilot > Azure > Direct.

# ── Option 1: GitHub Copilot SDK (uses your Copilot subscription) ──
# Requires: npm install @github/copilot-sdk
# Requires: Copilot CLI installed and authenticated (copilot login)
# Each model call consumes 1 premium request from your subscription.
# USE_COPILOT_SDK=true

# ── Option 2: Azure Foundry (enterprise, billed via Azure) ──
# Get these from Azure Portal → Your Foundry Resource → Keys and Endpoint
# AZURE_API_KEY=your-azure-api-key
# AZURE_API_BASE=https://your-resource-name.services.ai.azure.com/anthropic

# ── Option 3: Direct Anthropic API (simplest, pay-as-you-go) ──
# Get this from https://console.anthropic.com → Settings → API Keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ── Optional: OpenAI fallback (not yet implemented) ──
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
